  "description": "<h4>Application:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>BMW 135i (E82/E88) N54B30 3.0L Turbo, 2008-2010</li>\n<li>BMW 535i / 535ix (E60/E61) N54B30 3.0L Turbo, 2008-2010</li>\n<li>BMW Z4 sDrive35i / sDrive35is (E89) N54B30 3.0L Turbo, 2009-2016</li>\n<li>BMW X6 xDrive35i (F71) N54B30 3.0L Turbo, 2008-2010</li>\n<li>BMW 740i / 740Li (F01/F02) N54B30 3.0L Turbo, 2010-2012</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"color: red;\"><strong>NOT fit 335i</strong></p>\n<h4>Features:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>17T design with upgraded forged billet compressor wheel, comparable in flow to a 17T turbo</li>\n<li>Enhances vehicle performance and engine power, capable of handling up to 750HP</li>\n<li>Component balanced, dynamically balanced more precisely than VSR HIGH SPEED using state-of-the-art balancing machine, avg 0.5 mg or less</li>\n<li>Billet wastegate flapper valves (stainless steel with thicker rod)</li>\n<li>Some modifications required for installation due to larger compressor housing inlet</li>\n<li>2 inch (55mm) intake hose needed to match larger inlet</li>\n<li>The accessories shown in the photos are included</li>\n<li>1-year warranty for any manufacturing defect</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Technical Specifications:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Upgraded Forged Billet Compressor Wheel: 12 blades (6+6), size: 43.4 x 58 mm</li>\n<li>Turbine Wheel: 9 blades, size: 41.2 x 47.2 mm</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Turbo Part Numbers:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>49131-07000, 49131-07001, 49131-07006, 49131-07007, 49131-07010</li>\n<li>49131-07011, 49131-07015, 49131-07016, 49131-07107, 49131-07018</li>\n<li>49131-07019, 49131-07030, 49131-07031, 49131-07040, 49131-07041</li>\n<li>49131-07065, 49131-07066, 49131-07067, 49131-07068, 49131-07069</li>\n<li>49131-07075, 49131-07076, 49131-07077, 49131-07078, 49131-07079</li>\n<li>49131-07161, 49131-07170, 49131-07180, 49131-07205, 49131-07206</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>O.E.M Numbers:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>11654564711, 11654564710, 11657563685, 11657563686, 11657583863</li>\n<li>11657583864, 11657593015, 11657593016, 11657649289, 11657649290</li>\n<li>4564710, 4564711, 7583863, 7583864, 7593015, 7593016, 7563685, 7563686</li>\n<li>7649289, 7649290</li>\n</ul>",
